<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٤ - عبد الله بن لَهيعة.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>أخرجه أحمد <span class="c2">(١٤٧١٩)</span> والطبراني في <span class="c1">"الأوسط"</span> <span class="c2">(٩٠٦٦)</span> والآجري <span class="c2">(٨٣٧)</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
